%h2
  Registration

  %p
    The ANRW 2022 will be held at the Sheraton Philadelphia Downtown in
    Philadelphia, PA, USA. 
    The workship is co-located with the IETF-114 meeting which runs from
    23-29 July 2022 in the same venue.

  %p
    All attendees
    %b must
    register for the ANRW. Registration provides for admittance to the ANRW
    and to the IETF welcome reception and tutorials on Sunday 24 July 2022.

  %p
    Registration for in-person attendance at the ANRW costs $150 USD for
    all attendees that are
    %b not
    also attending the IETF-114 meeting. Registration for the ANRW is free
    of charge for those who have registered for in-person attendance at
    IETF-114 for the full week, on a day pass for the day of the workshop,
    or as a full-time student.  The IETF registration fee is $150 USD for
    full-time students, and covers attendance at all IETF working groups,
    tutorials, and other sessions for the entire week, as well as the ANRW. 

  %p
    You
    %b
      do not
    need to register for IETF-114 in order to attend ANRW. If you do want
    to attend both IETF and ANRW, remember to come back here and register
    for ANRW after completing your IETF registration.

  %p
    At least one author of each accepted paper
    %b
      must
    register for the ANRW, and attend in-person to present their paper.

  %p
    The ANRW will be streamed live and recorded. Remote participation will
    be provided using the IETF remote participation system. You can find
    more details and information on how to register for remote participation
    on the IETF-114 meeting page.

  %p
    %a{ :href => "/anrw/2022/travelgrants.html"} Travel Grants
    are available to support attendance at the ANRW 2022.








